36
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,829
But I hope you can trust me.

37
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,750
I'll help you.

38
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:54,430
Dr. Peng,

39
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:56,710
will I ever get well?

40
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:00,200
Anxiety disorders caused my brother's suicide.

41
00:04:00,690 --> 00:04:02,470
He took his own life in his room

42
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:04,590
