43
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:07,360
Why did your brother commit suicide?

44
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,350
Because of a woman.

45
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:11,220
A bad woman.

46
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:14,270
That temptress is to blame for my brother's death!

47
00:04:14,670 --> 00:04:17,240
She went out of her way to make my brother fall in love with her.

48
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,810
