52
00:04:35,409 --> 00:04:36,490
Ning Mochen...

53
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:39,230
Ning Mochen...

54
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:43,190
My brother said his personal tragedy was caused by her.

55
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,560
My brother hated her.

56
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,159
Ning Mochen...

57
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:57,480
Who is this Ning Mochen

58
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,800
you're talking about?

59
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,660
Ningmei Jewelry...

60
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,230
Ning Mochen...

61
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,340
Dr. Peng,

62
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,930
when I was asleep,

63
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:20,900
I had a dream where my brother told me a name.

64
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:21,910
What name?

65
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,340
Ning Mochen.

66
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,130
Do you know her?

67
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,380
No.

68
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,050
Is it important?

69
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:35,810
I think

70
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:38,680
I should avenge my brother.

71
00:05:43,470 --> 00:05:44,270
Ms. Zhao,

72
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:47,310
your brother took his own life.

73
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,420
It was that woman

74
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:51,430
